---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import content from '../data/content.json';
const { brand } = content;
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy – SiteForge"
  description="Privacy Policy for SiteForge web design services."
>

<!-- Nav -->
<header id="site-nav" class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-300">
  <div class="mx-4 mt-3 rounded-2xl bg-[#0A0F1E]/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 h-14 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5 flex-shrink-0" aria-label="SiteForge home">
        <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-brand to-brand-cyan flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs font-display">S</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-display font-bold text-base text-white tracking-wide">{brand.name}</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">← Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Content -->
<main class="bg-white min-h-screen pt-28 pb-24">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold text-brand bg-brand-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-ink mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink/40 font-medium">SiteForge &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last updated: March 7, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="prose-legal">

      <section>
        <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>SiteForge is a web design service that builds professional websites for local service businesses. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@siteforgeonline.com">hello@siteforgeonline.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following information when you interact with our website or start a project:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Business name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This information may be collected through our contact form or during the onboarding process.</p>
        <p>Payment information is processed securely by Stripe. SiteForge does not see or store your credit card details.</p>
        <p>We may collect basic anonymous usage data if analytics tools are used on the website.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Information You Voluntarily Provide</h2>
        <p>You may choose to provide personal information when contacting SiteForge through our website, email, or during the onboarding process. This may include your name, business name, email address, phone number, and details about your business or website project.</p>
        <p>By submitting this information, you consent to SiteForge using it solely to respond to your inquiry, deliver services, or communicate with you regarding your project.</p>
        <p>SiteForge does not intentionally collect sensitive personal information unless voluntarily provided by the client.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information collected for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>To deliver your website project</li>
          <li>To communicate with you regarding your project</li>
          <li>To send invoices or payment links via Stripe</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We only use your information as necessary to provide and manage our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may share limited information with third-party services required to operate our business:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> – payment processing</li>
          <li><strong>FormSubmit</strong> – contact form delivery</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These providers process information only as necessary to perform their services. SiteForge does not sell personal data to third parties. These third-party providers have their own privacy policies governing how they handle data.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Project files and communication related to your project may be stored for up to 2 years after project completion. After this period, the information may be permanently deleted.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request access to or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting <a href="mailto:hello@siteforgeonline.com">hello@siteforgeonline.com</a>. We will make reasonable efforts to respond to such requests within a reasonable timeframe.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website does not use tracking cookies. We do not use advertising pixels, behavioral tracking tools, or retargeting technologies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>SiteForge may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If changes are made, the updated version will be published on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. External Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites not operated by SiteForge. SiteForge has no control over and assumes no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>11. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>SiteForge services are not intended for individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child under 13 has provided personal information through this website, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@siteforgeonline.com">hello@siteforgeonline.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>12. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact: <a href="mailto:hello@siteforgeonline.com">hello@siteforgeonline.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>13. Data Security</h2>
        <p>While we take reasonable steps to protect personal information, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. Therefore, SiteForge cannot guarantee absolute security of any information transmitted through the website.</p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer nav -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-ink/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-sm text-ink/40">© <span id="year"></span> SiteForge. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/terms" class="text-sm text-ink/40 hover:text-brand transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-brand hover:text-brand-dark font-medium transition-colors">← Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>

</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A0F1E;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #F1F5F9;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    list-style: disc;
  }
  .prose-legal ul li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #3B82F6;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>
